"/> You shouldn't jump to any conclusions, at least not yet.

According to eBay's records they've been registered since
July 2002, and maintained a decent selling record (not perfect
by any stretch, but still ok) through the first part of June 2003.
It appears something drastic happened and they started
cancelling orders.

If it was outright fraud eBay would have pulled the plug on
them a long time ago. So I'd say wait a week or two and
see if eBay sends you any more information.

